<li><a href="https://launchpad.net/compiz">Compiz</a> - OpenGL compositing window manager. It has a plug-in system to be changed at runtime.</li>
<h2>Applications</h2><h4>Not based on any desktop environment</h4>
<li><a href="https://pwmt.org/projects/zathura/">Zathura</a> - Highly customizable document viewer. It provides a minimalistic and space saving interface as well as an easy usage that mainly focuses on keyboard interaction.</li>
